<main id="main-content">
<section class="page-header"><div class="container"><h1>Contact</h1><p>Write to us or call us. We answer ourselves, not an answering machine.</p></div></section>
<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;"><div class="container">
<div class="contact-grid">
<!-- Left Col: Info -->
<div>
<h2>Where we are</h2>
<hr class="decorative-line" style="margin-left: 0;"/>
<div style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
<h3 style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Address</h3>
<p>Agriturismo La Collina dei Lecci<br/>Località S. Donato, 21<br/>53037 San Gimignano SI<br/>Tuscany, Italy</p>
</div>
<div style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
<h3 style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Phone</h3>
<p><a href="tel:+390550000000">+39 055 000 0000</a></p>
<p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-text-muted);">We answer from 8am to 8pm. Out of hours, please leave a message.</p>
</div>
<div style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
<h3 style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Email</h3>
<p><a href="mailto:info@lacollinadeilecci.com">info@lacollinadeilecci.com</a></p>
<p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-text-muted);">We usually reply on the same day.</p>
</div>
<div>
<h3 style="margin-bottom: 8px;">How to arrive</h3>
<p><strong>From Florence (45 mins):</strong> Florence-Siena dual carriageway, exit at Poggibonsi Nord. Follow signs for San Gimignano. After about 10 km, turn towards Località S. Donato.</p>
<p><strong>From Siena (35 mins):</strong> Siena-Florence dual carriageway, exit at Poggibonsi Nord. Follow signs for San Gimignano.</p>
<p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-top: 8px;">The final stretch is a comfortable unpaved country road, accessible with any car.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Right Col: Form -->
<div>
<h2>Write to us</h2>
<hr class="decorative-line" style="margin-left: 0;"/>
<form class="contact-form" id="contact-form" novalidate="">
<div class="form-group">
<label for="contact-name">Name</label>
<input autocomplete="name" id="contact-name" name="name" placeholder="Your name" required="" type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="form-group">
<label for="contact-email">Email</label>
<input autocomplete="email" id="contact-email" name="email" placeholder="Your email" required="" type="email"/>
</div>
<div class="form-group">
<label for="contact-message">Message</label>
<textarea id="contact-message" name="message" placeholder="Tell us what you have in mind — dates, number of guests, questions..." required=""></textarea>
</div>
<button class="btn btn--primary" type="submit">Send message</button>
<div aria-live="polite" class="form-message" id="form-message" role="status"></div>
</form>
</div>
</div>
